            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Pompeius Felix <lb n="3"/>vixit annis XXXVII <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ensibus</ex></expan> II diebus VIII <lb n="5"/>fecit <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Martial<supplied reason="lost">is</supplied> <lb n="6"/>civi et amico <lb n="7"/>bene merenti
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Rémy - Ballet - Ferber note that the inscription has sometimes been considered false, but Hirschfeld, who saw it, doesn&amp;apos;t consider this possibility.</p>
            </div>
